      "title": "ProSight Native Complex Down Analysis of Aquaporin Z",
      "additionalAttributes": [],
      "projectDescription": "In this dataset, we analyzed Aquaporin Z using native mass spectrometry. The data was then input into ProSight Native to determine the protein complex composition.",
      "sampleProcessingProtocol": "E. coli expressed Aquaporin Z was analyzed using a Thermo Q Exactive UHMR.",
      "dataProcessingProtocol": "The complex workflow in ProSight Native was used to perform deconvolution of intact complex and subunit mass spectra. Fragmentation data was searched in the subunit portion of ProSight Native. A final composition was determined by using the deconvolution and search results.",
